{"data":[{"name":"99:1","price":"当大地猛烈地震动，","arabic":"إِذَا زُلۡزِلَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ زِلۡزَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6139,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:2","price":"抛其重担，","arabic":"وَأَخۡرَجَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ أَثۡقَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6140,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:3","price":"人们说：“大地怎么啦?”","arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6141,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:4","price":"在那日，大地将报告它的消息。","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ تُحَدِّثُ أَخۡبَارَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6142,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:5","price":"因为你的养主已启示了它；","arabic":"بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوۡحَىٰ لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6143,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:6","price":"在那日，人们将纷纷地离散，以便他们得见自己行为〔的报应〕。","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَصۡدُرُ ٱلنَّاسُ أَشۡتَاتٗا لِّيُرَوۡاْ أَعۡمَٰلَهُمۡ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6144,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:7","price":"行一个微尘重的善事者，将见其善报;","arabic":"فَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيۡرٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6145,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"99:8","price":"作一个微尘重的恶事者，将见其恶报。","arabic":"وَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٖ شَرّٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6146,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah","Chapter Az-Zalzalah","Zalzalah","Surah Zalzalah","Chapter Zalzalah","Az Zalzalah","Surah Az Zalzalah","Chapter Az Zalzalah","Surah 99","Chapter 99","The Earthquake"